### Events Endpoints Testing
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@userToken = Bearer YOUR_USER_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get All Events
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 2. Get All Events with Pagination and Sorting
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events?page=0&size=10&sortBy=date&sortDir=asc
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 3. Get Upcoming Events
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/upcoming
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 4. Get Event by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/1
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 5. Get Event by ID with Attendees
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/1?includeAttendees=true
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 6. Create New Event (with form data - multipart)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="event"
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Community Outreach Event",
  "description": "Join us for a community service event to help local families",
  "date": "2025-02-15T10:00:00",
  "endDate": "2025-02-15T16:00:00",
  "location": "Community Center",
  "maxAttendees": 50,
  "requiresApproval": false,
  "isPublic": true,
  "tags": ["community", "service", "outreach"]
}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 7. Create New Event (JSON only - no image)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events
Authorization: {{userToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="event"
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Bible Study Group",
  "description": "Weekly Bible study and discussion group",
  "date": "2025-01-20T19:00:00",
  "endDate": "2025-01-20T21:00:00",
  "location": "Fellowship Hall",
  "maxAttendees": 20,
  "requiresApproval": false,
