### 9. Delete Event
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/events/1
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 10. Join Event
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events/1/join
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 11. Leave Event
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events/1/leave
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 12. Approve User for Event (Organizer Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events/1/approve/2
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 13. Get User's Event Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/1/status
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 14. Get My Events (Events I Organized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/my-events
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 15. Get My Events with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/my-events?page=0&size=5&sortBy=date&sortDir=desc
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 16. Get Events I'm Attending
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/attending
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 17. Get Events I'm on Waiting List For
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/waiting-list
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 18. Search Events
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/search?query=community
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 19. Search Events by Location
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/search?query=hall
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### 20. Search Events by Title
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/search?query=bible
Authorization: {{userToken}}